Product Description

Product Description This Full HD LED monitor with 50,000,000:1 high contrast ratio and HDMI interface is optimised for a fine image and colour quality. This approach extends to the sturdy stand and slim profile without compromising style in ensuring stability and durability. It features Smart View technology that can adjust colour parameters to deliver the same image quality and colours with straight viewing.Hole Spacing : VESA standard 100 x 100 mm
